{"tid":1550812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到時幾時先會全民武裝？","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:18:07.000Z","uid":233442,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b72f67ad4bbf202ae63c2e7996554b45a97795c7","tid":1550812,"uid":233442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:51:44.000Z","msg":"好似烏克蘭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算當防備都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時都唔覺香港人咁大忍耐力<br />\n每日睇住新聞見到我地班年輕人被施暴虐打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通撤回真係分化到大家？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可"},{"pid":"080adbcb88123cbcc86f908322279a2cf9115b0e","tid":1550812,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"6c4032cc122650a33dee82665d90ae0b3a847ca7","tid":1550812,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f312c07463a05f74da2be7bc2c12509c5efe074","tid":1550812,"uid":112124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"呢個問題香港人唔會面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e193fccabf9104c4575ec45565588c4b35a4012","tid":1550812,"uid":166734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:53:41.000Z","msg":"香港人怕事 膽小<br />\n才助長軍政府<br />\n<br />\n死人都係得把口"},{"pid":"e69850e057bdd6e5e01203cc4949e713bdc6827d","tid":1550812,"uid":233442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"自推到有人見到，班勇武真係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcce1a47c61f26b21d7f62edf0b0e20ffb06717","tid":1550812,"uid":166734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"仲要唔肯承認唔夠膽，內弱。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話對付軍政府<br />\n<br />\n藍屍都唔夠膽對付。<br />\n仲話要對付黑社會？！"},{"p